<br>
I'm not trying to be an jerk, nor was I or am I making any comments about the relative strength of different guilds (which is why I am puzzled by Nyca's post).  <br>
<br>
As I have pointed out already, I'm well aware it isn't reserved all the time or even most of the time.  I'm aware that it can be reserved and I could if I wanted try to go about reserving it.  <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>I just want to know why it makes sense for the post-revamp hate to remain on the calendar system. </strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->  If nobody wants to answer, oh well. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/btherathetravelagency.showUserPublicProfile?gid=saediien>Saediien</A> at: 8/12/03 4:03 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/btherathetravelagency.showUserPublicProfile?gid=seerfamily>Seer Family</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User and Abuser!</span><br>  Posts: 522<br> <font color=#00FFFF>(8/12/03 4:05 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ftherathetravelagencyfrm50.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=935.topic&index=20>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Plane of Hate</span><hr size=1> yep Circle of Virtue and Mirth and Mayhem...we ubah<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :rolleyes --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/eyes.gif ALT=":rolleyes"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
